  "faq": [
    {
      "question": {
        "en-US": "Which phrases are most useful for a Vietnam itinerary with flights and buses?",
        "zh-CN": "如果越南行程里有飞机和卧铺巴士，最值得先准备哪类短语？"
      },
      "answer": {
        "en-US": "Start with transport, dining, and hotel. That covers airport arrivals, Grab, sleeper bus questions, check-in, and most first-day food orders in Vietnam.",
        "zh-CN": "建议先看交通、餐饮和酒店三组，基本就能覆盖机场落地、Grab、卧铺巴士询问、入住办理，以及第一天大部分点餐场景。"
      }
    },
    {
      "question": {
        "en-US": "Why do phrase cards help so much in Vietnam?",
        "zh-CN": "为什么在越南旅行时，短语卡会特别有帮助？"
      },
      "answer": {
        "en-US": "Because tone and pronunciation matter, and many travel interactions happen quickly. Showing a short phrase card often works better than trying to repeat the same sentence several times.",
        "zh-CN": "因为越南语对声调和发音很敏感，而且很多旅行场景节奏都很快。直接展示一张简短短语卡，往往比反复重复同一句话更有效。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
